 If you <EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e68">do</EVENT> the uh alternative extreme, you do n't <EVENT class="OCCURRENCE" eid="e69">save</EVENT> as many lives in <TIMEX3 functionInDocument="NONE" temporalFunction="false" tid="t118" type="DURATION" value="PXY">the
